#: /tmp/cicero-RKYt/release-8.2.xml:4658(para) 
msgid "Improve recovery from a crash during <acronym>WAL</acronym> replay (Simon)"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/cicero-RKYt/release-8.2.xml:4662(para) 
msgid "The server now does periodic checkpoints during <acronym>WAL</acronym> recovery, so if there is a crash, future <acronym>WAL</acronym> recovery is shortened. This also eliminates the need for warm standby servers to replay the entire log since the base backup if they crash."
