#: /tmp/cicero-RKYt/release-8.2.xml:4672(para) 
msgid "Improve reliability of long-term <acronym>WAL</acronym> replay (Heikki, Simon, Tom)"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/cicero-RKYt/release-8.2.xml:4677(para) 
